3
00:01:56,720 --> 00:01:58,470
Which one of you is Arlong?!

4
00:01:59,100 --> 00:02:01,480
My name happens to be Arlong.

5
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:02,940
I'm Luffy.

6
00:02:03,310 --> 00:02:04,900
Luffy?

7
00:02:04,900 --> 00:02:06,560
And what are you, exactly?

8
00:02:06,900 --> 00:02:08,440
A pirate!

9
00:02:08,780 --> 00:02:10,490
Hey, hold up, you bastard.

10
00:02:11,570 --> 00:02:13,320
Where do you think you're goin'?

11
00:02:14,030 --> 00:02:18,700
You need to run things
by us first, kiddo.

12
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,200
Hey, now!

13
00:02:20,200 --> 00:02:21,790
If you don't stop...

14
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:24,290
Move!

15
00:02:27,290 --> 00:02:29,340
What does a pirate want with me?

16
00:02:51,320 --> 00:02:53,570
Just who the hell are you?!

17
00:02:58,620 --> 00:02:59,490
Luffy...

18
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:02,120
Help me...

19
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:04,960
I won't let you make
our navigator cry!

20
00:03:04,960 --> 00:03:05,750
Why, you...

21
00:03:05,750 --> 00:03:08,380
How dare you insult Arlong!

22
00:03:10,460 --> 00:03:13,340
Butt out, shrimp!

23
00:03:16,340 --> 00:03:17,390
Sheesh...

24
00:03:17,930 --> 00:03:20,260
You just had to run
ahead by yourself...

25
00:03:20,260 --> 00:03:22,470
I can handle myself just fine.

26
00:03:22,470 --> 00:03:26,600
Idiot! When did I say
I was worried about you?!

27
00:03:27,310 --> 00:03:29,860
I just don't want you
hogging all the fun.

28
00:03:29,860 --> 00:03:31,150
Oh, makes sense!

29
00:03:31,150 --> 00:03:36,320
W-Well, I don't mind
letting you hog it all!

30
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:39,030
How awfully generous of you.

31
00:03:40,370 --> 00:03:44,330
That's the guy!
The mysterious swordsman!

32
00:03:44,330 --> 00:03:45,830
That's Roronoa Zoro.

33
00:03:45,830 --> 00:03:51,250
Yeah? Yeah, I thought so!
He tricked me!

34
00:03:51,250 --> 00:03:52,840
He really took me for a ride...

35
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:55,800
No, wait... Didn't I give him a ride?

36
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:57,380
Look! It's that long-nosed guy!

37
00:03:58,550 --> 00:04:02,220
D-Didn't Nami kill him?!

38
00:04:02,220 --> 00:04:04,520
It's just as I suspected, then.

39
00:04:05,390 --> 00:04:08,190
The girl turned against us!

40
00:04:16,240 --> 00:04:18,150
Hey! Who are those guys?!

41
00:04:18,950 --> 00:04:19,990
– Hold it!
– Hold it!

42
00:04:21,910 --> 00:04:24,160
He sent Arlong flying!

43
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:25,870
Unbelievable!

44
00:04:27,370 --> 00:04:29,710
No ordinary human could do that!

45
00:04:29,710 --> 00:04:31,670
They're...

46
00:04:32,170 --> 00:04:35,380
Do you still want to
try and break in now?

47
00:04:35,380 --> 00:04:38,760
In a fight like this, there's
nothing you guys can do.

48
00:04:38,760 --> 00:04:40,640
You'll only get in their way!

49
00:04:40,640 --> 00:04:44,390
B-But... why are they fighting?

50
00:04:44,390 --> 00:04:47,020
What reason do they have to fight?!

51
00:04:47,020 --> 00:04:48,560
What reason?

52
00:04:51,150 --> 00:04:52,860
Big Sis Nami was crying!

53
00:04:55,980 --> 00:04:59,610
What other reason do they need
to put their lives on the line?

54
00:05:03,830 --> 00:05:06,540
A pirate, huh? I see...

55
00:05:06,540 --> 00:05:09,410
So that's what this is about.

56
00:05:10,330 --> 00:05:13,000
You were after Nami
from the very start.

57
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:14,170
But really...

58
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:18,510
what can you four lowbred
worms possibly do?!

59
00:05:20,760 --> 00:05:24,300
Fools! You're not worth Arlong's time!

60
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:26,430
I know just the guy to take you on!

61
00:05:34,860 --> 00:05:36,070
Don't tell me...

62
00:05:36,070 --> 00:05:37,730
It's coming!

63
00:05:41,320 --> 00:05:43,820
Wh-Wh-Wh-What's going on?!

64
00:05:43,820 --> 00:05:46,660
Rise, Momoo!

65
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:55,250
A-A monster!

66
00:05:55,250 --> 00:05:58,750
That's the monster from
the Grand Line that destroyed Gosa!

67
00:06:10,270 --> 00:06:12,060
It's here!

68
00:06:13,730 --> 00:06:15,230
Th-That's...

69
00:06:15,230 --> 00:06:16,520
...the fearsome Momoo!

70
00:06:22,650 --> 00:06:23,910
Oh, that guy?

71
00:06:23,910 --> 00:06:25,620
He's with the fishmen?

72
00:06:29,410 --> 00:06:32,370
Wait! Momoo! Where are you going?!

73
00:06:32,790 --> 00:06:36,000
Hey! Stop! Get back here! Momoo!

74
00:06:37,750 --> 00:06:40,960
Momoo. What do you
think you're doing?

75
00:06:45,300 --> 00:06:50,470
I mean, if you wanna run away,
I won't stop you.

76
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:54,520
Well, Momoo?

77
00:07:01,730 --> 00:07:03,690
Here it comes! Here it comes!

78
00:07:03,690 --> 00:07:04,700
Alright!

79
00:07:04,700 --> 00:07:06,530
Follow Momoo!

80
00:07:10,910 --> 00:07:13,330
I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
I'm sorry! I'm sorry!

81
00:07:16,960 --> 00:07:19,670
I'll do it! This is a waste of time!

82
00:07:28,760 --> 00:07:31,220
What is he up to this time?!

83
00:07:31,220 --> 00:07:34,100
I've got a bad feeling about this...

84
00:07:51,870 --> 00:07:53,740
His arms stretched!

85
00:07:55,960 --> 00:07:58,250
Devil fruit powers?!

86
00:07:58,250 --> 00:07:59,290
What?!

87
00:07:59,290 --> 00:08:00,130
Who cares?!

88
00:08:00,130 --> 00:08:00,710
Get him!

89
00:08:03,340 --> 00:08:04,170
Whoa! Run!

90
00:08:04,170 --> 00:08:06,220
What? What's he doing?!

91
00:08:06,220 --> 00:08:08,720
I dunno, but it doesn't look good!

92
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:15,060
Gum-Gum...

93
00:08:16,060 --> 00:08:21,150
Pinwheel!

94
00:08:30,990 --> 00:08:34,830
I didn't come here to fight these guys!

95
00:08:35,370 --> 00:08:37,750
If I'm gonna beat anyone up...

96
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:40,080
it's gonna be you!

97
00:08:40,790 --> 00:08:42,960
What a coincidence...

98
00:08:44,590 --> 00:08:48,720
I was just thinking about
killing you, too.

99
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:51,140
That was dangerous, you moron!

100
00:08:51,140 --> 00:08:53,760
Are you trying to kill us, too?!

101
00:08:58,890 --> 00:09:01,270
Such destructive power...

102
00:09:01,650 --> 00:09:05,650
I can't believe a human exists
who can throw that giant beast!

103
00:09:05,980 --> 00:09:08,820
Are my eyes playing tricks on me?

104
00:09:11,700 --> 00:09:14,370
How dare you hurt our brothers!

105
00:09:15,330 --> 00:09:19,620
It seems like we're going
to have to fight, too.

106
00:09:19,620 --> 00:09:23,290
Looks like we need to teach them
the differences between our races.

107
00:09:23,290 --> 00:09:26,250
The real players are
finally ready, huh?

108
00:09:30,050 --> 00:09:32,760
Please sit back and relax, Arlong.

109
00:09:32,760 --> 00:09:39,480
If you go on a rampage,
you'll end up leveling Arlong Park.

110
00:09:42,480 --> 00:09:45,150
We'll take care of these guys!

111
00:09:45,150 --> 00:09:48,110
Sure, do whatever you want.

112
00:09:49,030 --> 00:09:51,280
Yikes...!

113
00:09:51,900 --> 00:09:54,820
Hey. Guys. Hold on a second.

114
00:09:54,820 --> 00:09:57,280
That octopus is up to something.

115
00:09:57,280 --> 00:10:00,500
Octopus is best served
sliced, salted, and boiled.

116
00:10:00,500 --> 00:10:04,710
Add some olive oil and paprika,
and it pairs perfectly with a drink.

117
00:10:04,710 --> 00:10:07,130
Hey, I'm kinda in trouble here.
Can I have a sec?

118
00:10:07,130 --> 00:10:09,340
That's it! Kiss your sight goodbye!

119
00:10:09,340 --> 00:10:12,130
Octohachi Black!

120
00:10:16,550 --> 00:10:18,810
You idiot! Why didn't you dodge?!

121
00:10:20,520 --> 00:10:22,770
I can't see!

122
00:10:23,850 --> 00:10:25,560
Now to finish you off!

123
00:10:28,570 --> 00:10:30,530
Hey, Luffy! Run!

124
00:10:31,360 --> 00:10:33,490
Y-Yeah... Th-That's the problem..

125
00:10:34,660 --> 00:10:37,410
I don't think I can run!

126
00:10:38,410 --> 00:10:39,700
Huh?!

127
00:10:40,080 --> 00:10:42,710
M-My feet are stuck!

128
00:10:42,710 --> 00:10:45,670
You're the one who
stuck them in the ground!

129
00:10:45,670 --> 00:10:47,920
Why is he always like this...?

130
00:10:49,380 --> 00:10:52,760
Octohachi Black on the Rocks!

131
00:11:09,860 --> 00:11:11,900
What a pain.

132
00:11:12,530 --> 00:11:15,280
Sanji! That was amazing!

133
00:11:15,280 --> 00:11:19,450
Seems like I chose
one hell of an idiot for a captain.

134
00:11:19,780 --> 00:11:20,950
You said it.

135
00:11:20,950 --> 00:11:23,500
He's... so cool!

136
00:11:23,830 --> 00:11:29,920
But he's a hundred times better than
a bunch of thugs who'd hurt a lady.

137
00:11:29,920 --> 00:11:31,670
Lady?

138
00:11:33,010 --> 00:11:36,220
Can't believe you'd
break in here for one lousy girl.

139
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:38,180
Lousy girl?

140
00:11:38,800 --> 00:11:41,350
Just try and insult
Nami one more time.

141
00:11:41,350 --> 00:11:45,230
I'll pan-fry you in butter and turn
you into fishman meunière!

142
00:11:45,230 --> 00:11:48,850
You seem somewhat
skilled for a human.

143
00:11:48,850 --> 00:11:52,980
But chivalry from a pirate
is bound to be half-hearted.

144
00:11:54,900 --> 00:11:58,240
Go ahead and see if my chivalry
is half-hearted or not.

145
00:11:58,240 --> 00:12:01,990
I spent half my life raised by
a gristly old pirate.

146
00:12:04,660 --> 00:12:09,630
It appears you don't know the true
power of the fishman race.

147
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:14,840
No good. They're still pretty stuck.

148
00:12:15,510 --> 00:12:17,800
Still?! They're still stuck?!

149
00:12:19,090 --> 00:12:21,050
Yep, still stuck.

150
00:12:21,050 --> 00:12:23,810
I don't think pulling me
is gonna get them unstuck.

151
00:12:23,810 --> 00:12:27,270
Are you even trying?! Are you even
trying to get your legs out?!

152
00:12:27,270 --> 00:12:32,230
Who do they think they are,
playing around in Arlong Park?!

153
00:12:32,730 --> 00:12:34,320
I'll kill them!

154
00:12:35,570 --> 00:12:38,200
Come on, come on!
Get unstuck already!

155
00:12:40,160 --> 00:12:41,620
Get back here!

156
00:12:41,620 --> 00:12:42,990
Hey, octopus.

157
00:12:43,490 --> 00:12:45,450
They're busy right now.

158
00:12:46,580 --> 00:12:48,410
I'll take you on.

159
00:12:49,790 --> 00:12:53,040
Roronoa Zoro! That's right! I forgot!

160
00:12:53,040 --> 00:12:55,300
How dare you trick me!

161
00:12:58,760 --> 00:13:03,760
That's right! Not to mention
all my brethren you cut down!

162
00:13:03,760 --> 00:13:06,180
I don't care. That's all old news.

163
00:13:06,770 --> 00:13:10,940
It doesn't really matter
why you want to kill me.

164
00:13:11,650 --> 00:13:13,900
The situation has changed.

165
00:13:14,440 --> 00:13:17,110
You're not trying
to crush us anymore.

166
00:13:17,110 --> 00:13:19,860
We're trying to crush you!

167
00:13:19,860 --> 00:13:24,030
A-Alright, Zoro!
The octopus is all yours! Nice!

168
00:13:24,700 --> 00:13:26,330
Luffy!

169
00:13:32,500 --> 00:13:33,790
I'm back...

170
00:13:36,800 --> 00:13:38,460
Why, you...

171
00:13:38,460 --> 00:13:40,420
My bad...

172
00:13:40,420 --> 00:13:44,430
Seems you really do
want me to kill you.

173
00:13:49,270 --> 00:13:53,230
Wasn't that the guy
who saved Mr. Gen?

174
00:13:56,020 --> 00:13:58,190
You're the people from
Cocoyashi Village!

175
00:13:58,190 --> 00:13:59,320
Oh?

176
00:13:59,320 --> 00:14:04,200
Judging from those weapons,
I take it this is a rebellion?

177
00:14:04,660 --> 00:14:05,490
Then you're all–

178
00:14:05,490 --> 00:14:07,160
Fire Star!

179
00:14:07,740 --> 00:14:09,200
Big Bro Usopp!

180
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:15,580
You're dealing with me!

181
00:14:17,670 --> 00:14:20,550
If you wanna die that badly,
I'll finish you right now!

182
00:14:23,510 --> 00:14:25,930
Just who is that boy?

183
00:14:25,930 --> 00:14:29,680
He's brave one minute, then runs away
the next. He's a peculiar one...

184
00:14:32,980 --> 00:14:34,560
Get back here, big nose!

185
00:14:34,560 --> 00:14:36,610
You're one to talk, big mouth!

186
00:14:37,820 --> 00:14:40,190
How are these guys pirates?

187
00:14:44,990 --> 00:14:49,830
You're all pathetic. Move.
I can't watch another second of this.

188
00:14:50,120 --> 00:14:54,330
Arlong! We asked you
not to go on a rampage!

189
00:14:54,330 --> 00:14:58,790
I won't. I just thought up a fun game.

190
00:15:00,270 --> 00:15:02,170
I'm gonna kick...

191
00:15:02,670 --> 00:15:05,010
your ass!

192
00:15:06,430 --> 00:15:10,140
Do you seriously think
you can beat us?

193
00:15:10,140 --> 00:15:12,100
So what if we do?

194
00:15:12,100 --> 00:15:14,350
We sure do, dummy!

195
00:15:14,350 --> 00:15:15,560
Now let go!

196
00:15:15,560 --> 00:15:17,520
Sounds like he has something to say.

197
00:15:25,450 --> 00:15:27,110
What the...?!
What the...?! What the...?!

198
00:15:29,120 --> 00:15:31,950
People with devil fruit
powers can't swim!

199
00:15:32,370 --> 00:15:36,710
Though, even people without powers
would sink in this situation!

200
00:15:38,210 --> 00:15:40,130
He's gonna throw him into the sea?!

201
00:15:41,000 --> 00:15:43,880
Gum-Gum Pistol!

202
00:15:46,300 --> 00:15:49,260
Oww!

203
00:15:49,260 --> 00:15:50,350
Fool.

204
00:15:51,260 --> 00:15:53,720
Damn you!

205
00:15:53,720 --> 00:15:55,680
How pointless.

206
00:16:00,730 --> 00:16:01,360
Luffy!

207
00:16:01,650 --> 00:16:02,860
You bastard!

208
00:16:13,080 --> 00:16:13,910
I'll save–

209
00:16:13,910 --> 00:16:15,790
Idiot! Don't get worked up!

210
00:16:16,410 --> 00:16:19,370
They want us to go in the water!

211
00:16:19,370 --> 00:16:23,000
Fishmen have the obvious
advantage in an underwater fight!

212
00:16:23,750 --> 00:16:26,170
There's only one way to save Luffy!

213
00:16:27,340 --> 00:16:30,680
Take these guys down in a flash
and hop in the water?

214
00:16:32,050 --> 00:16:34,140
Let's do it! There's no time!

215
00:16:34,140 --> 00:16:34,680
Yeah!

216
00:16:34,680 --> 00:16:38,640
Just how long will
the rubber man last?

217
00:16:38,640 --> 00:16:40,690
Oh, so that's the game?

218
00:16:40,690 --> 00:16:41,940
I see.

219
00:16:45,230 --> 00:16:46,820
You can have the fish.

220
00:16:47,530 --> 00:16:49,660
You can cut and trim the octopus.

221
00:17:02,540 --> 00:17:06,260
Man... This is bad. I feel so weak...

222
00:17:07,380 --> 00:17:10,090
What do we do?!
He's helpless down there!

223
00:17:10,090 --> 00:17:11,840
Big Bro Luffy's going to die!

224
00:17:20,390 --> 00:17:22,770
They can't even breathe underwater.

225
00:17:23,060 --> 00:17:25,770
Humans are utterly pitiful creatures!

226
00:17:27,730 --> 00:17:28,860
Bring it on!

227
00:17:28,860 --> 00:17:30,780
I'll cross swords with you, octofreak!

228
00:17:35,280 --> 00:17:36,660
Sure, I'm game!

229
00:17:36,990 --> 00:17:39,160
I'll take care of you in five seconds!

230
00:17:40,000 --> 00:17:41,080
No, three seconds!

231
00:17:41,670 --> 00:17:43,380
Don't be in such a rush.

232
00:17:44,000 --> 00:17:48,130
It doesn't matter what you do!
None of you are leaving here alive!

233
00:18:01,560 --> 00:18:06,480
I-I'm dead meat!

234
00:18:06,820 --> 00:18:09,690
Give us five seconds, Luffy!
We'll beat them and save you!

235
00:18:10,070 --> 00:18:11,570
Octohachi Black!

236
00:18:19,790 --> 00:18:22,040
My hair! You bastard!

237
00:18:22,040 --> 00:18:24,830
I'm gonna...

238
00:18:25,210 --> 00:18:26,130
forgive you.

239
00:18:26,130 --> 00:18:28,420
It's just hair, so it'll grow back.

240
00:18:28,420 --> 00:18:28,840
Huh?

241
00:18:29,210 --> 00:18:30,460
Roronoa Zoro!

242
00:18:30,460 --> 00:18:34,470
You can't cut me
because I have six hands.

243
00:18:34,470 --> 00:18:36,550
Go ahead! Try to cut me!

244
00:18:36,550 --> 00:18:37,140
Octofreak!

245
00:18:37,510 --> 00:18:44,060
Octo Triple Razor Sharp Blade Grab!

246
00:18:38,100 --> 00:18:44,060
Octo Triple Razor Sharp Blade Grab!

247
00:18:39,010 --> 00:18:44,060
Octo Triple Razor Sharp Blade Grab!

248
00:18:39,850 --> 00:18:44,060
Octo Triple Razor Sharp Blade Grab!

249
00:18:40,600 --> 00:18:44,060
Octo Triple Razor Sharp Blade Grab!

250
00:18:41,430 --> 00:18:44,060
Octo Triple Razor Sharp Blade Grab!

251
00:18:42,270 --> 00:18:44,060
Octo Triple Razor Sharp Blade Grab!

252
00:18:43,100 --> 00:18:44,060
Octo Triple Razor Sharp Blade Grab!

253
00:18:46,400 --> 00:18:48,150
Ouch!

254
00:18:48,150 --> 00:18:49,900
I don't have time to play with you!

255
00:18:51,530 --> 00:18:53,360
He throws me off my rhythm.

256
00:18:54,030 --> 00:18:55,740
Could he possibly...

257
00:18:55,740 --> 00:18:57,740
Blink and you're dead!

258
00:18:57,740 --> 00:19:00,740
Fish shouldn't be fighting a cook!

259
00:19:01,240 --> 00:19:02,870
We're running out of time...

260
00:19:02,870 --> 00:19:04,040
There's no...

261
00:19:05,460 --> 00:19:07,040
Just drop dead already!

262
00:19:10,550 --> 00:19:13,050
Octohachi Number...

263
00:19:13,050 --> 00:19:14,550
Nine!

264
00:19:16,050 --> 00:19:18,720
What are you doing?!
Get down here already!

265
00:19:20,220 --> 00:19:21,970
You damn octopus!

266
00:19:23,140 --> 00:19:26,230
That octopest! He's just
goofing around and stalling!

267
00:19:26,230 --> 00:19:30,770
Still, if he goes in the water now, he'll
be dragged to the bottom of the sea!

268
00:19:30,770 --> 00:19:33,900
But at this rate,
Big Bro Luffy's going to die!

269
00:19:33,900 --> 00:19:35,860
We've got to do something!

270
00:19:35,860 --> 00:19:36,410
Yeah!

271
00:19:36,410 --> 00:19:36,860
Wait!

272
00:19:36,860 --> 00:19:38,530
– Ouch!
– Ouch!

273
00:19:38,530 --> 00:19:42,080
How are you going to be any help
with injuries like those?

274
00:19:43,200 --> 00:19:45,910
You can't do much
when you're hurt like this.

275
00:19:46,460 --> 00:19:49,580
If you're talking about that
rubber boy, I'll go rescue him.

276
00:19:49,580 --> 00:19:51,040
Y-You will?

277
00:19:51,040 --> 00:19:52,300
Mr. Gen!

278
00:19:52,300 --> 00:19:53,210
I'll go, too!

279
00:19:53,210 --> 00:19:54,380
I'll go as well!

280
00:19:54,380 --> 00:19:55,720
Me, too!

281
00:19:55,720 --> 00:20:01,010
No! If too many of us go to rescue him,
the fishmen are bound to notice.

282
00:20:01,010 --> 00:20:03,560
We'd just be making
their job even harder!

283
00:20:03,560 --> 00:20:04,270
Mr. Gen!

284
00:20:04,270 --> 00:20:08,900
It'll be pointless if we end up
interfering with their fight.

285
00:20:08,900 --> 00:20:10,230
So I'll do it alone.

286
00:20:11,230 --> 00:20:13,360
Sorry... Thank you!

287
00:20:13,360 --> 00:20:14,940
We'll leave it to you.

288
00:20:14,940 --> 00:20:16,820
Sorry, but please be quick.

289
00:20:17,320 --> 00:20:18,030
Wait!

290
00:20:19,110 --> 00:20:20,950
Mr. Gen, I'll go too.

291
00:20:20,950 --> 00:20:23,080
Nojiko, you're injured!

292
00:20:23,080 --> 00:20:26,830
Those guys are fighting
for my little sister!

293
00:20:27,120 --> 00:20:28,120
Mr. Gen!

294
00:20:29,330 --> 00:20:31,290
Okay. Come on!

295
00:20:31,290 --> 00:20:32,130
Let's hurry!

296
00:20:32,130 --> 00:20:32,790
Okay!

297
00:20:34,500 --> 00:20:35,920
I'm sorry...

298
00:20:35,920 --> 00:20:38,720
If only we were a little stronger...

299
00:20:39,180 --> 00:20:42,140
Please... save Big Bro!

300
00:20:46,220 --> 00:20:50,100
Roronoa Zoro! Do you mind if I ask
you a question? You don't, right?

301
00:20:50,100 --> 00:20:52,230
I heard you use the three-sword style.

302
00:20:52,230 --> 00:20:53,980
Why are you using only one sword?

303
00:20:53,980 --> 00:20:56,610
One already seems like
overkill for the likes of you!

304
00:20:56,610 --> 00:20:59,200
Sh-Shut up! I'm not
taking this seriously!

305
00:20:59,200 --> 00:21:03,830
Actually, there's a reason that a human
swordsman could never defeat me.

306
00:21:03,830 --> 00:21:05,910
Wanna hear what it is?
You do, don't you?

307
00:21:05,910 --> 00:21:09,160
When you hear it, you'll be
surprised, scared, blown away!

308
00:21:09,920 --> 00:21:13,290
Dammit! I can't be in pain right now!

309
00:21:21,340 --> 00:21:22,800
I knew it. It's those wounds...

310
00:21:24,930 --> 00:21:26,770
from your fight with Hawk Eye!

311
00:21:27,350 --> 00:21:28,480
– Big Bro!
– Big Bro!

312
00:21:31,690 --> 00:21:34,310
Look! This is my true form!

313
00:21:34,310 --> 00:21:37,150
Here comes Hachi,
user of the six-sword style!

314
00:21:37,150 --> 00:21:41,030
Hey! That's not when you're
supposed to fall! Don't mock me!

315
00:21:43,820 --> 00:21:44,990
Ah! Big Bro!

316
00:21:44,990 --> 00:21:47,240
So he really was in pain!

317
00:21:47,240 --> 00:21:48,410
Yeah.

318
00:21:48,410 --> 00:21:52,920
His injuries would kill a normal person
or leave them bedridden for half a year!

319
00:21:52,920 --> 00:21:53,710
What?!

320
00:21:56,630 --> 00:21:58,590
I knew something was off.

321
00:21:58,590 --> 00:22:02,260
Acting all nonchalant
after a fight like that...

322
00:22:02,260 --> 00:22:03,640
Is he an idiot or what?!

323
00:22:11,270 --> 00:22:14,520
I thought I told you not to blink.

324
00:22:14,520 --> 00:22:16,730
I'm a 40th-degree
black belt in Fishman Karate.

325
00:22:16,730 --> 00:22:19,230
Wh-What?

326
00:22:19,230 --> 00:22:20,690
Someone went flying?!

327
00:22:20,690 --> 00:22:22,400
B-Big Bro?!

328
00:22:22,400 --> 00:22:23,820
Big Bro Cook!

329
00:22:26,490 --> 00:22:29,490
Big Bro Cook!

330
00:22:30,290 --> 00:22:32,750
He's been taken care of, Arlong.

331
00:22:32,750 --> 00:22:34,710
What do we do with Roronoa Zoro?

332
00:22:34,710 --> 00:22:39,750
Just toss him in the sea.
What weaklings... How boring!

333
00:22:42,880 --> 00:22:43,720
That's all?

334
00:22:44,050 --> 00:22:47,550
Geez, they sure wreaked some havoc.

335
00:22:47,550 --> 00:22:49,260
It's no big deal.

336
00:22:49,260 --> 00:22:52,480
It'll take more than this
to bring down Arlong Park.

337
00:22:52,480 --> 00:22:53,690
Indeed...

338
00:22:55,310 --> 00:22:57,400
How dare you, Roronoa Zoro!

339
00:22:57,400 --> 00:23:01,030
You died from shock before I,
the great swordsman, could attack you?!

340
00:23:01,030 --> 00:23:04,610
History would've remembered you
had you fallen to my six-sword style.

341
00:23:04,610 --> 00:23:08,240
Well, struggle all you want
or even flip the world on its head,

342
00:23:08,240 --> 00:23:14,290
no human could ever lay a hand
on me, the wielder of six swords!

343
00:23:22,710 --> 00:23:24,220
Stop it, Hachi.

344
00:23:24,220 --> 00:23:28,720
I know how you feel, but we'll be in
big trouble if you actually go on a rampage.

345
00:23:28,720 --> 00:23:30,390
Do you want to destroy Arlong Park?

346
00:23:32,140 --> 00:23:34,140
N-No. Sorry.

347
00:23:34,810 --> 00:23:37,730
I got a little too worked up.

348
00:23:37,730 --> 00:23:38,900
Don't get carried away.

349
00:23:38,900 --> 00:23:40,900
My bad, my bad.

350
00:23:41,780 --> 00:23:44,610
Six-sword style, huh? What a joke!

351
00:23:50,830 --> 00:23:52,290
Big Bro!

352
00:23:54,540 --> 00:23:56,750
Roronoa Zoro!

353
00:23:56,750 --> 00:23:59,080
I'll tell you one thing, octopus.

354
00:23:59,670 --> 00:24:02,590
There's a man I need to meet.

355
00:24:03,170 --> 00:24:05,670
And until I see him again...

356
00:24:07,930 --> 00:24:11,720
even Death himself can't take my life!

357
00:24:28,450 --> 00:24:30,240
He's still alive!

358
00:24:30,240 --> 00:24:32,410
Big Bro! Big Bro Cook!

359
00:24:33,490 --> 00:24:37,620
That fishman's punch
was 40th-degree, huh?

360
00:24:38,250 --> 00:24:43,340
Then all those kicks from the old fart
must've been 400th-degree.

361
00:24:44,050 --> 00:24:46,510
This guy won't give up!
